    {
      "Text": "Security update for Mesa",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for Mesa fixes the following issue:\n\n- CVE-2026-40393: out-of-bounds memory access can occur in WebGPU because the amount of to-be-allocated data depends on\n  an untrusted party (bsc#1261998).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
